OL,3,CFive arrested after stabbing in
OL,4,CFinchley
OL,6,FPolice have arrested five men after a
OL,7,Fstabbing in West Finchley on Saturday
OL,8,Fnight.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to Ballards Lane
OL,11,Fjust after 7pm, where they found a man
OL,12,Fin his 40s with stab injuries.
OL,14,FIt comes in the same week that
OL,15,Fhundreds of Iranians in Finchley
OL,16,Fturned out to celebrate the death of
OL,17,FIran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah ali
OL,18,FKhamenei.
OL,20,FA London Ambulance Service
OL,21,Fspokesperson said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
