OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773162679
OL,3,CFive arrested after stabbing in
OL,4,CFinchley
OL,6,F"We were called at 6.52pm on Saturday
OL,7,F7 March to reports of a stabbing in
OL,8,FBallards Lane, Finchley, N3.
OL,10,F"We sent resources including ambulance
OL,11,Fcrews, a clinical team manager, an
OL,12,Fadvanced paramedic practitioner and an
OL,13,Fincident response officer.
OL,15,F"We treated a man at the scene before
OL,16,Ftaking him to a London major trauma
OL,17,Fcentre."
OL,19,FThe victim was taken to hospital where
OL,20,Fhis condition was not thought to be
OL,21,Flife-threatening or life-changing.
